overrun a head
Homonym Number:
Word Class:phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:[sheepdogs] to make too long an arc when heading sheep.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
